ilities, though they come at a steep price.\\n\\nFinding the Cloud Nomads is no small feat, unless they choose to anchor for trade, their skyborne homes remain hidden among the clouds."]]'],title:"Book Title",author:"Monk Zaccarius",generation:1,resolved:1},"minecraft:custom_name":'{"text":"Cloud Nomads","italic":false,"color":"#66ffff"}',"minecraft:lore":['{"text":"A description of the Cloud Nomads factions.","italic":false,"color":"gray"}']}}}

